Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: Starting at 4th level, a dragon warrior can endow her weapons with elemental energy while she wields them in battle. This energy is of the same type as her breath weapon. At 4th level, this bonus deals an extra 1d6 points of energy damage, and this extra damage increases to 2d6 at 9th level. This ability lasts for one hour per class level at a time (no limit on uses).
Use: Selected.